AAA MASONRY, INC. and the Travelers Insurance Company, Petitioners, v. Enrique JUSTIZ et al., Respondents. No. 42889. Supreme Court of Florida. Feb. 19, 1973. CARLTON, C. J., and ERVIN, ADKINS, BOYD and DEKLE, JJ., concur. ROBERTS and McCAIN, JJ.,. dissent.
